{"tid":1897423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】央視主持人：中國應為「添亂」向世界道歉","createTime":"2020-02-25T17:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T17:40:04.000Z","uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc0ed52e65f92db38a335b4380be6bce6f087b9","tid":1897423,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:14:23.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】央視主持人：中國應為「添亂」向世界道歉<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e5476615e00e37651d95451.jpg/QQOwYwwlk3_c8UO0AIKABHcjHUalPmJ5PRbO6T0Wzuk?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e5476615e00e37651d95451.jpg%2FQQOwYwwlk3_c8UO0AIKABHcjHUalPmJ5PRbO6T0Wzuk%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=edf80677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新冠肺炎（COVID-19）疫情持續，針對中國的防疫抗疫，美國《華爾街日報》早前刊發《中國是真正的亞洲病夫》一文引起軒然大波。<br />\n<br />\n日前，一位央視主持人在微博表示，雖然「東亞病夫」的牌匾「已經踢碎」，但中國應該為此次給全球「添亂」道歉。<br />\n<br />\n言論在網絡引起爭議，有反對者稱，病毒是「天災」，而不是中國「添亂」。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒《華爾街日報》早前刊登題為《中國是真正的「亞洲病夫」》（China Is the Real Sick Man of Asia）的評論文章，被指帶有種族歧視，涉嫌辱華。中國外交部19日表示，鑑於《華爾街日報》迄今仍在推諉、搪塞，既未公開正式道歉，也未查處相關責任人，決定即日起吊銷《華爾街日報》三名駐京記者的記者證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e54745d6f91ff14194bdd5b.jpg/680bOROS8IkFF5sqgw2v37goWtDs_-zw8G7p0vBu6dI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e54745d6f91ff14194bdd5b.jpg%2F680bOROS8IkFF5sqgw2v37goWtDs_-zw8G7p0vBu6dI&h=4dd4502c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e3ce0b7fe36d22bbeb14778.jpg/sCnNAg_AuUoCIfJWoH8Cj3k6kVUkQDMEGwr1PxsK9T8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e3ce0b7fe36d22bbeb14778.jpg%2FsCnNAg_AuUoCIfJWoH8Cj3k6kVUkQDMEGwr1PxsK9T8&h=4eaaf3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e54745d6f91ff14194bdd5c.jpg/7u28bZ0gAs9INkQcqbZdKRLAa5Yq5PBjLZEB8S2RAfE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e54745d6f91ff14194bdd5c.jpg%2F7u28bZ0gAs9INkQcqbZdKRLAa5Yq5PBjLZEB8S2RAfE&h=6a34056c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名微博認證為「央視主持人」的網絡大V「阿丘」20日發布微博指，中國人應該道歉，理由是中國給世界「添亂了」。他說，「此時，雖然東亞病夫的牌匾早已踢碎了一個多世紀了，但我們可不可以說話語調稍温和並帶些歉意，不慫也不豪橫地把口罩戴起來，向世界鞠個躬，說聲：對不起，給你們添亂了？」<br />\n<br />\n阿丘言論引起爭議，有網民對其言論表示支持，亦有許多網民表示反對，認為病毒是天災，是全人類所要面對的敵人，而阿丘的言論是很危險的，「為潛在的排華行為提供道德依據」。<br />\n<br />\n目前，阿丘已刪除相關微博。"},{"pid":"72d66273d9afbe965ad0731aaa2be01a25bd1600","tid":1897423,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"為世界添煩添亂"},{"pid":"a34ca49831b946eb75ccc44bf5c8f182c59ebabc","tid":1897423,"uid":65556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:40:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾好聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ob6s0qjjKhY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOb6s0qjjKhY&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=cdcc7bb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ob6s0qjjKhY</a><br />\n\t</span>"}]}